high_descs: Go straight, go around the kitchen island, then go to the sink next to the fridge.
Take the fork from in the sink.
Turn around, then go left to go toward the microwave.
Put the fork in the wine glass, in the rightmost cabinet above the microwave.
Take the wine glass from the cabinet.
Turn around, then go straight, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the wine glass in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a wine glass with a fork in it in the sink.

high_descs: Move to the sink to the right of the fridge
Pick up a fork from the sink
Move to the stove to the right
Put the fork inside a glass in the cabinet
Pick up the glass and close the door to the cabinet
Move to the sink to the right of the fridge
Place the glass inside of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a fork in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the counter
Grab the fork that is in the sink
Turn to the right
Walk straight to the cabinet that is above the microwave
Open the door to the above cabinet
Stick the fork in the cabinet
Get the glass that is in the cabinet and take it to the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting away clean dishes, gathering dirty dishes
